title: War of the Roses: She Thinks Her Friend's Boyfriend is Cheating
description: Leigh has a friend named Brad who was in an accident that left him in a wheelchair but he is still the kindest person ever and dates a guy named Thomas.  Leigh has been hearing things about Thomas that leads her to believe he might not be being faithful to Brad, so now she wants to see is Thomas is cheating on her good friend Brad.
